01:02:10.708 --> 01:02:12.250
- the Nintendo version
was very neutered

01:02:13.333 --> 01:02:15.458
The blood was turned
into like a sweat.

01:02:16.916 --> 01:02:18.500
- People who played it
knew what was happening.

