and do all this other stuff.

01:02:44.291 --> 01:02:48.916
And yeah. so the Genesis
version was the version.

01:02:48.916 --> 01:02:51.833
as far as anyone I
knew was concerned.

01:02:51.833 --> 01:02:54.375
This NES version
